{\displaystyle F(t,x(t),x^{(1)}(t),\dots ,x^{(n)}(t))=0\quad \left(x^{(k)}(t):={\frac {\mathrm {d} ^{k}}{\mathrm {d} t^{k}}}x(t),\,\mathrm {for} ~\,k=0,1,\dots ,n.\right)}



